strategies: I tried to think about whether I have heard of the city before and what states or countries it might be in.
familiar: How certain I am that I know about the city and how much I know about the city.
memorable: A rough estimation of how likely I would be to remember the name after an extended period of time.
unique: A rough estimation of how many cities have this name; or how common the words that make up the name are.
realistic: How likely the name is to be of a real city.
